.cursor/openclaw-bridge/
sajtmaskin.zip


# --- Dossier-pipeline (skrap-/enrich-output, embeddings, repo-cache) ---
data/dossiers/_raw/playwright-catalog-light.json
data/dossiers/_raw/_enriched/
data/dossiers/_raw/_curation-queue.md
data/dossiers/_raw/_import-summary.json
data/dossiers/_raw/*/skiss.json
